## Create Sender ID

```shell
curl "https://api.batchpack.co/v1/company/buy_sender_id/BTOKEN" \
-H "apikey: API_KEY" \
-d '{"senderId": "COCACOLA", "comments": "My new sms id for promotional messages", "category": "Marketing"}' \
-X POST
```

> Response:

```json
{
  "id": 7,
  "sender_id": "SAM",
  "comment": "My new sms id for promotional messages",
  "status": "Pending Verification",
  "user_id": 1,
  "created_at": "2019-08-22T07:40:39.473Z",
  "updated_at": "2019-08-22T07:40:39.473Z",
  "category": "Marketing"
}
```

Alphanumeric sender IDs are used for branded one-way messaging. Alphanumeric sender IDs cost $1. Without a verified senderID you may not be able to send a message using batchpack or keep using the default BATCHPACK


### HTTP Request

`POST https://api.batchpack.co/v1/company/buy_sender_id/BTOKEN`

### URL Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
senderId | The Alphanumeric sender ID
comments | Any thing random

